    <h1>History!</h1>
    <p>Much like all stories, the origin of <strong class="m">Mushroom</strong> and <strong class="j">Jupiter</strong> started with your typical childhood explanation</p>
    <blockquote>When a mommy and a mommy love each other ... very ... mu....?</blockquote>
    <p>Wait that's not right. How can two hamsters be born to two moms?</p>
