        <p>Jupiter took to her enclosure pretty quickly, while Mushroom seemed absolutely pissed to be here. She explored a bit, but mostly just hunkered down in her ceramic mushroom hideout. There was a bit of opening up, and a good amount of pee on the wheel, but something just didn't seem right with him.</p>
        <p>Wait did you just say <em>him</em>? I thought you had two girls?. Yes, dear reader, I did.</p>
